videos.description: Devin Sibley dribbles into traffic and spins to make the tough and-1 through contact.
videos.headline: Furman's Sibley finishes strong through contact

videos.description: Jordan Bone finds Jordan Bowden and he euro-steps his way for a nice layup.
videos.headline: Tennesse's Bowden smooth around the basket

videos.description: Devin Sibley weaves his way through defenders in transition and finishes the and-1 bucket through contact.
videos.headline: Furman's Sibley makes impressive layup

videos.description: Grant Williams backs down his defender and floats it in to put Tennessee ahead 63-61.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Williams gets the go-ahead bucket
